import React from 'react' import ReactDom from 'react-dom' import {add,sub,mult,div} from './App' ReactDOM.render( <>
  1. sum of two number is {add(40, 50)}
  2. sub of two number is {sub(60, 50)}
  3. div of two number is {div(40, 4)}
  4. mul of two number is {mult(40, 5)}
,document.getElementById('root') );
